<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>EDGE — We Build Brands That Win</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root{
  --purple:#6A0DAD;
  --dark:#1a0a2e;
  --light:#faf9fc;
  --muted:#6b6280;
}

*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{
  font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
  background:var(--light);
  color:var(--dark);
}

/* NAV */
nav{
  position:fixed;
  top:0;width:100%;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  padding:1rem 6%;
  background:white;
  border-bottom:1px solid #eee;
  z-index:100;
}
.logo{
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-weight:800;
  color:var(--purple);
}
nav a{
  text-decoration:none;
  color:var(--muted);
  margin-left:20px;
  font-size:0.9rem;
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
  padding:120px 6% 80px;
  max-width:900px;
}
.hero h1{
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4.5rem);
  line-height:1.1;
}
.hero span{
  color:var(--purple);
}
.hero p{
  margin-top:20px;
  color:var(--muted);
  max-width:500px;
}
.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  margin-top:30px;
  padding:12px 28px;
  border-radius:40px;
  background:var(--purple);
  color:white;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:600;
}

/* SECTION */
section{
  padding:80px 6%;
}
h2{
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-size:2rem;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

/* SERVICES */
.services{
  display:grid;
  gap:20px;
}
.card{
  background:white;
  padding:25px;
  border-radius:15px;
  border:1px solid #eee;
}
.card h3{
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* PORTFOLIO */
.port{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:15px;
}
.port div{
  background:#ddd;
  height:180px;
  border-radius:12px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  color:#666;
  font-size:0.9rem;
}

/* CTA */
.cta{
  text-align:center;
  background:var(--dark);
  color:white;
  padding:80px 20px;
}
.cta a{
  background:white;
  color:var(--purple);
  margin-top:20px;
  display:inline-block;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
  padding:40px 6%;
  font-size:0.8rem;
  color:#777;
}

@media(max-width:600px){
  .port{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">EDGE</div>
  <div>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#portfolio">Work</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>We Build <span>Brands</span><br>That Bring Clients.</h1>
  <p>If your brand is not attracting customers, it is costing you money. We fix that with strategic design.</p>
  <a href="https://wa.me/2348165925204" class="btn">Start Now</a>
</div>

<section id="services">
  <h2>What We Do</h2>
  <div class="services">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Brand Identity</h3>
      <p>Logos, colours and systems that position your business properly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Design</h3>
      <p>Social media, flyers and visuals that pull attention.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Brand Growth</h3>
      <p>We guide how your brand shows up so clients trust and buy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="portfolio">
  <h2>Selected Work</h2>
  <div class="port">
    <div>Brand Project</div>
    <div>Logo Design</div>
    <div>Flyer Design</div>
    <div>Social Media</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <h2>Your Brand Is Either Helping You Or Killing You</h2>
  <p>Fix it now or keep losing clients.</p>
  <a href="https://wa.me/2348165925204" class="btn">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>WhatsApp: +234 816 592 5204</p>
</section>

<footer>
  © 2026 EDGE Creative Studio
</footer>

</body>
</html>                    
